tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE error_correction_codes (
    code_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    code_name VARCHAR(255),
    code_description TEXT,
    qubit_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (qubit_id) REFERENCES qubits(qubit_id)
);

CREATE TABLE error_correction_procedures (
    procedure_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    procedure_name VARCHAR(255),
    procedure_details TEXT,
    code_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (code_id) REFERENCES error_correction_codes(code_id)
);

CREATE TABLE qubits_error_correction (
    qubit_id INT,
    code_id INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (qubit_id, code_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (qubit_id) REFERENCES qubits(qubit_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (code_id) REFERENCES error_correction_codes(code_id)
);

CREATE TABLE qubit_error_corrections (
  qec_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  qubit_id INT NOT NULL,
  ecp_id INT NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (qubit_id) REFERENCES qubits(qubit_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (ecp_id) REFERENCES error_correction_procedures(ecp_id)
);

CREATE TABLE code_qubit_mapping (
  mapping_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  ecc_id INT NOT NULL,
  qubit_id INT NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (ecc_id) REFERENCES error_correction_codes(ecc_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (qubit_id) REFERENCES qubits(qubit_id)
);
